# Welcome!

Here you can find the documentation of some projects I made on GitHub.

# Projects
### [USTCORi Physics Experiment Simulation System Assistant](https://github.com/ProfFan/PhysicsExprSimulationTest)
An assistant for the USTCORi Experiment Simulation System. Use at your own risk.

### [PhabriTeX](/phabritex)

Phabritex is my rough effort for adding LaTeX support into the Phabricator system.

### [Bootstrap-Han](/bootstrap-han)

Bootstrap 4 + Han.css for beautiful Chinese web design.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
